Package robosky.structurehelpers.structure.processor

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AirGroundReplacementProcessor
    A structure processor that only replaces certain block states with one of two block states depending on whether it is placed in the air or in the ground.
    AirGroundReplacementProcessor.Entry
    Replacement entry.
    PartialBlockState
    A representation of a set of BlockState matching a Block and Property values.
    PartialBlockState.Builder
    Builder for PartialBlockState.
    WeightedChanceProcessor
    Replaces given block with another randomly chosen from the given pool.
    WeightedChanceProcessor.Builder
    Builder for WeightedChanceProcessor.
    WeightedChanceProcessor.Entry
    A record of a PartialBlockState with a weight.
